void listsTextFilesRecursively(){
    List<TextFile> files = fileSource.listFilesRecursively();

    assertThat(
        files,
        hasExactlyIgnoringOrder(
            fileNamed("one"),
            fileNamed("two"),
            fileNamed("three"),
            fileNamed("four"),
            fileNamed("five"),
            fileNamed("six"),
            fileNamed("seven"),
            fileNamed("eight"),
            fileNamed("deepfile.json")));
  }

void list_all_files(){
    List<TextFile> files = fileSource.listFilesRecursively();

    assertThat(
        files,
        hasExactlyIgnoringOrder(
            fileNamed("one"),
            fileNamed("two"),
            fileNamed("three"),
            fileNamed("four"),
            fileNamed("five"),
            fileNamed("six"),
            fileNamed("seven"),
            fileNamed("eight"),
            fileNamed("deepfile.json")));
  }
